114
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:46,470
From the future?

115
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,070
[2024]

116
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:59,070
Are you living alone?

117
00:07:02,670 --> 00:07:04,110
