142
00:09:07,830 --> 00:09:08,510
This is?

143
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:10,630
This was your room in the past.

144
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:12,870
I left the room just as it is

145
00:09:13,950 --> 00:09:15,230
