417
00:22:44,910 --> 00:22:45,980
This place is great.

418
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:47,430
[It's remote and spacious.]

419
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,750
[Even the loan sharks can't find us here.]

420
00:22:50,180 --> 00:22:50,870
