after it closed down.

516
00:28:07,870 --> 00:28:08,510
I don't care anymore.

517
00:28:08,990 --> 00:28:09,590
Let's head there for now.

518
00:28:12,870 --> 00:28:13,350
Brother Feng,

519
00:28:13,630 --> 00:28:14,350
